[[File:Map Canton Luzern Bezirke.png|thumb|Districts of Canton Lucerne]]
The Canton is divided into 5 districts termed ''<U+00C4>mter'':
*[[Luzern (Amt)|Amt Luzern]] with capital [[Lucerne|Luzern]]
*[[Hochdorf (Amt)|Amt Hochdorf]] with capital [[Hochdorf, Lucerne|Hochdorf]]
*[[Sursee (Amt)|Amt Sursee]] with capital [[Sursee]]
*[[Willisau (Amt)|Amt Willisau]] with capital [[Willisau]]
*[[Entlebuch (Amt)|Amt Entlebuch]] with capital [[Sch<U+00FC>pfheim]]

