==Demographics==
The population is mainly German ({{as of|2000|lc=on}}, 89%<ref>{{cite web | last = Federal Department of Statistics | title = Wohnbev<U+00F6>lkerung nach Sprachen | year = 2004 | url = http://www.bfs.admin.ch/bfs/portal/de/index/themen/01/05/blank/key/sprachen.html | format = Interactive Map | accessdate = 2009-01-15 }}</ref> speaking and the vast majority is Roman Catholic (71% {{as of|2000|lc=on}}, with a 12% [[Protestantism|Protestant]] minority.<ref>{{cite web | last = Federal Department of Statistics | title = Wohnbev<U+00F6>lkerung nach Religion | year = 2004 | url = http://www.bfs.admin.ch/bfs/portal/de/index/themen/01/05/blank/key/religionen.html | format = Interactive Map | accessdate = 2009-01-15 }}</ref>)

